snippet.title: Galacticare Gameplay Trailer | Demo Available June 19th
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/494730/Galacticare/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=gameplaytrailer&utm_campaign=demo

Follow us on tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@galacticare
Talk to us on discord: https://discord.gg/brightrockgames
Follow us on twitter: https://twitter.com/galacticare
Check out the development blog: https://blog.galacticare.com

Remember to wishlist to get notified when the game launches!

Save the galaxy - one patient at a time! As the new director of Galacticare, you will build and manage a series of hospitals to keep your patients alive for as long as possible - for money! And also because it’s the right thing to do.

Galacticare is a sci-fi hospital management game with complex mechanics and a rich narrative, releasing late 2023.

Wishlist on PlayStation 5: https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10008023/
Xbox X|S/One: https://www.xbox.com/en-gb/games/store/galacticare/9pb14ld018sm
Wishlist on GOG: https://www.gog.com/en/game/galacticare
